    <item>
      <title>以色列的中央银行负责人批评内塔尼亚胡的预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/israel-s-central-bank-chief-criticizes-netanyahu-s-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列的中央银行州长批评了政府的预算，该预算在周二得到了议会的批准，称在18个月的战争产生的激增后，它将无法迅速降低债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/israel-s-central-bank-chief-criticizes-netanyahu-s-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 12:06:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自2023年以来，英国住房租金以最慢的年速度增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/uk-housing-rents-increase-at-slowest-annual-pace-since-2023</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据官方数据，英国住房租金以自2023年以来最慢的速度增长，这给了压痛的租户带来一些缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/uk-housing-rents-increase-at-slowest-annual-pace-since-2023</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 11:33:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏丹军队说，首都的机场从民兵中夺回</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/sudanese-army-says-capital-s-airport-recaptured-from-militia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名官员说，苏丹的陆军夺回了喀土穆国际机场，距离首都的快速支援部队靠近，这将是两年的内战的转折点。]]></description>
